Nairobi speaker Alex Magelo (pictured)yesterday urged supporters to ignore &ldquo;detractors spreading lies&rdquo; that he has retired from politics.He said he is in the race for Kajiado West MP. Magelo said his opponents fear him and have been spreading rumours to weaken his bid. He spoke at Kiserian Market.He urged residents to register to vote. The month-long mass voter registration will end on Tuesday. With only four days left, the speaker urged the state to fast track issuance of IDs so residents get voter&rsquo;s cards.